{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1039,"text":"The power of yet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":3944,"text":"I heard about a high school in Chicago"},{"time":6547,"text":"where students had to pass\na certain number of courses to graduate,"},{"time":10723,"text":"and if they didn't pass a course,\nthey got the grade \"Not Yet.\""},{"time":16246,"text":"And I thought that was fantastic,"},{"time":18699,"text":"because if you get a failing grade,\nyou think, I'm nothing, I'm nowhere."},{"time":22484,"text":"But if you get the grade \"Not Yet\","},{"time":25408,"text":"you understand that\nyou're on a learning curve."},{"time":28927,"text":"It gives you a path into the future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":32337,"text":"\"Not Yet\" also gave me insight"},{"time":36125,"text":"into a critical event early in my career,"},{"time":40425,"text":"a real turning point."},{"time":42598,"text":"I wanted to see"},{"time":44093,"text":"how children coped\nwith challenge and difficulty,"},{"time":49554,"text":"so I gave 10-year-olds"},{"time":52746,"text":"problems that were\nslightly too hard for them."},{"time":57085,"text":"Some of them reacted\nin a shockingly positive way."},{"time":62108,"text":"They said things like,\n\"I love a challenge,\""},{"time":66132,"text":"or, \"You know, I was hoping\nthis would be informative.\""},{"time":71751,"text":"They understood that their abilities\ncould be developed."},{"time":77710,"text":"They had what I call a growth mindset."},{"time":81581,"text":"But other students felt\nit was tragic, catastrophic."},{"time":86978,"text":"From their more fixed mindset perspective,"},{"time":91279,"text":"their intelligence\nhad been up for judgment,"},{"time":95225,"text":"and they failed."},{"time":98219,"text":"Instead of luxuriating\nin the power of yet,"},{"time":103319,"text":"they were gripped in the tyranny of now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":107722,"text":"So what do they do next?"},{"time":109674,"text":"I'll tell you what they do next."},{"time":112104,"text":"In one study, they told us\nthey would probably cheat the next time"},{"time":118341,"text":"instead of studying more\nif they failed a test."},{"time":122277,"text":"In another study, after a failure,"},{"time":125684,"text":"they looked for someone\nwho did worse than they did"},{"time":128823,"text":"so they could feel really\ngood about themselves."},{"time":133327,"text":"And in study after study,\nthey have run from difficulty."},{"time":139461,"text":"Scientists measured\nthe electrical activity from the brain"},{"time":145105,"text":"as students confronted an error."},{"time":148251,"text":"On the left, you see\nthe fixed-mindset students."},{"time":152311,"text":"There's hardly any activity."},{"time":154768,"text":"They run from the error."},{"time":157069,"text":"They don't engage with it."},{"time":159694,"text":"But on the right, you have the students\nwith the growth mindset,"},{"time":163365,"text":"the idea that abilities can be developed."},{"time":167308,"text":"They engage deeply."},{"time":169253,"text":"Their brain is on fire with yet."},{"time":172334,"text":"They engage deeply."},{"time":174652,"text":"They process the error."},{"time":176679,"text":"They learn from it and they correct it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181910,"text":"How are we raising our children?"},{"time":184600,"text":"Are we raising them\nfor now instead of yet?"},{"time":189783,"text":"Are we raising kids\nwho are obsessed with getting As?"},{"time":194921,"text":"Are we raising kids who don't know\nhow to dream big dreams?"},{"time":200375,"text":"Their biggest goal is getting the next A,\nor the next test score?"},{"time":207311,"text":"And are they carrying this need\nfor constant validation with them"},{"time":213973,"text":"into their future lives?"},{"time":216140,"text":"Maybe, because employers\nare coming to me and saying,"},{"time":220271,"text":"\"We have already raised a generation"},{"time":223767,"text":"of young workers\nwho can't get through the day"},{"time":227873,"text":"without an award.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":230462,"text":"So what can we do?"},{"time":233469,"text":"How can we build that bridge to yet?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":237277,"text":"Here are some things we can do."},{"time":239392,"text":"First of all, we can praise wisely,"},{"time":243391,"text":"not praising intelligence or talent."},{"time":246623,"text":"That has failed."},{"time":248457,"text":"Don't do that anymore."},{"time":250119,"text":"But praising the process\nthat kids engage in,"},{"time":254647,"text":"their effort, their strategies,\ntheir focus, their perseverance,"},{"time":258928,"text":"their improvement."},{"time":260601,"text":"This process praise creates kids\nwho are hardy and resilient."}]},{"cues":[{"time":267344,"text":"There are other ways to reward yet."},{"time":270503,"text":"We recently teamed up with game scientists"},{"time":274801,"text":"from the University of Washington"},{"time":276945,"text":"to create a new online math game\nthat rewarded yet."},{"time":282077,"text":"In this game, students were rewarded\nfor effort, strategy and progress."},{"time":288313,"text":"The usual math game"},{"time":290869,"text":"rewards you for getting answers\nright, right now,"},{"time":295299,"text":"but this game rewarded process."},{"time":298393,"text":"And we got more effort,"},{"time":301184,"text":"more strategies,"},{"time":303379,"text":"more engagement\nover longer periods of time,"},{"time":307297,"text":"and more perseverance when they hit\nreally, really hard problems."}]},{"cues":[{"time":313489,"text":"Just the words \"yet\"\nor \"not yet,\" we're finding,"},{"time":317107,"text":"give kids greater confidence,"},{"time":320575,"text":"give them a path into the future\nthat creates greater persistence."},{"time":327333,"text":"And we can actually\nchange students' mindsets."},{"time":332875,"text":"In one study, we taught them"},{"time":335236,"text":"that every time they push out\nof their comfort zone"},{"time":339717,"text":"to learn something new and difficult,"},{"time":343163,"text":"the neurons in their brain\ncan form new, stronger connections,"},{"time":348839,"text":"and over time, they can get smarter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":352288,"text":"Look what happened: In this study,"},{"time":354815,"text":"students who were not taught\nthis growth mindset"},{"time":358592,"text":"continued to show declining grades\nover this difficult school transition,"},{"time":364342,"text":"but those who were taught this lesson\nshowed a sharp rebound in their grades."},{"time":371318,"text":"We have shown this now,\nthis kind of improvement,"},{"time":377265,"text":"with thousands and thousands of kids,\nespecially struggling students."}]},{"cues":[{"time":384072,"text":"So let's talk about equality."},{"time":388291,"text":"In our country,\nthere are groups of students"},{"time":392553,"text":"who chronically underperform,"},{"time":395372,"text":"for example, children in inner cities,"},{"time":398544,"text":"or children on Native American\nreservations."},{"time":402027,"text":"And they've done so poorly for so long"},{"time":405788,"text":"that many people think it's inevitable."},{"time":409404,"text":"But when educators create\ngrowth mindset classrooms"},{"time":415319,"text":"steeped in yet,"},{"time":417714,"text":"equality happens."},{"time":420858,"text":"And here are just a few examples."},{"time":425027,"text":"In one year, a kindergarten class\nin Harlem, New York"},{"time":430938,"text":"scored in the 95th percentile"},{"time":435461,"text":"on the national achievement test."},{"time":438634,"text":"Many of those kids could not hold a pencil"},{"time":443020,"text":"when they arrived at school."},{"time":445776,"text":"In one year,"},{"time":448588,"text":"fourth-grade students\nin the South Bronx, way behind,"},{"time":453448,"text":"became the number one fourth-grade class\nin the state of New York"},{"time":459734,"text":"on the state math test."},{"time":463083,"text":"In a year, to a year and a half,"},{"time":467427,"text":"Native American students\nin a school on a reservation"},{"time":472801,"text":"went from the bottom\nof their district to the top,"},{"time":479824,"text":"and that district included\naffluent sections of Seattle."},{"time":485193,"text":"So the Native kids\noutdid the Microsoft kids."}]},{"cues":[{"time":493125,"text":"This happened because the meaning\nof effort and difficulty were transformed."},{"time":500921,"text":"Before, effort and difficulty"},{"time":504640,"text":"made them feel dumb,\nmade them feel like giving up,"},{"time":509841,"text":"but now, effort and difficulty,"},{"time":513623,"text":"that's when their neurons\nare making new connections,"},{"time":517159,"text":"stronger connections."},{"time":518968,"text":"That's when they're getting smarter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":522796,"text":"I received a letter recently\nfrom a 13-year-old boy."},{"time":528190,"text":"He said, \"Dear Professor Dweck,"},{"time":532209,"text":"I appreciate that your writing\nis based on solid scientific research,"},{"time":539182,"text":"and that's why I decided\nto put it into practice."},{"time":544188,"text":"I put more effort into my schoolwork,"},{"time":548099,"text":"into my relationship with my family,"},{"time":551054,"text":"and into my relationship\nwith kids at school,"},{"time":555302,"text":"and I experienced great improvement\nin all of those areas."},{"time":562440,"text":"I now realize I've wasted\nmost of my life.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":569357,"text":"Let's not waste any more lives,"},{"time":575096,"text":"because once we know"},{"time":578898,"text":"that abilities are capable of such growth,"},{"time":584304,"text":"it becomes a basic human right\nfor children, all children,"},{"time":591268,"text":"to live in places that create that growth,"},{"time":596933,"text":"to live in places filled with \"yet\"."}]},{"cues":[{"time":602987,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":604162,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}